          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A behavior defines the physics of a component and its context. The effect of a component behavior is persistent and occurs every time a person views the article. Compare that with an animation which happens just once each time a person views the component in your article.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
